! Links

* Wiki link: [[Some Tiddler]]
* Pretty link with caption: [[Caption|Target Tiddler]]
* Link to a system tiddler: [[$:/DefaultTiddlers]]
* CamelCase link: HelloThere
* Suppressed CamelCase: ~HelloThere
* External link: https://tiddlywiki.com
* External with caption: [[TW home|https://tiddlywiki.com]]
* Mailto link: [[Mail|mailto:nobody@example.com]]
* Link to a tiddler with a space: [[A Tiddler Title]]

!! Images

[img[Motovun Jack.jpg]]
[img[Tooltip text|Motovun Jack.jpg]]
[img width=200 height=150 class="tc-image" [Motovun Jack.jpg]]
[img width={{!!width}} [Motovun Jack.jpg]]
[img[https://tiddlywiki.com/favicon.ico]]

!! Transclusions

* Whole tiddler: {{MyTiddler}}
* With a template: {{MyTiddler||$:/core/ui/ViewTemplate}}
* Template only (current tiddler): {{||$:/core/ui/ViewTemplate}}
* Field reference: {{MyTiddler!!caption}}
* Current-tiddler field: {{!!title}}
* Index reference: {{MyData##key}}

Block-level transclusion alone on a line:

{{MyTiddler}}

{{MyTiddler||$:/core/ui/ViewTemplate}}

!! Filtered transclusions

* Inline: {{{ [tag[HelloThere]] }}}
* Inline with template: {{{ [tag[done]] ||$:/core/ui/ListItemTemplate }}}
* Inline with a custom separator: {{{ [tag[done]] +[sort[title]] :and[limit[5]] }}}

Block-level filtered transclusion:

{{{ [tag[done]sort[title]] }}}

{{{ [tag[done]sort[title]] ||$:/core/ui/ListItemTemplate }}}

!! Pretty extended links

* With tooltip via widget: <$link to="HelloThere" tooltip="Go there">A widget link</$link>
* Anchor-style external: <a href="https://tiddlywiki.com" class="tc-tiddlylink-external">raw anchor</a>
